{"tid":608295,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"利舞臺天降環保斗毀電車纜","createTime":"2018-03-28T04:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T07:19:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0518ab160b0bd57e7e52895ce88e1a9c2cc2ac42","tid":608295,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:34:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180328/20344987\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180328%2F20344987&d=widQjuZiYDQ1igVkOBXowL5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=64c9c1ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180328%2F20344987&h=3b28a75d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180328/20344987</a><br />\n<br />\n利舞臺天降環保斗毀電車纜<br />\n<br />\n4,458<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180328/large/28la8p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180328%2Flarge%2F28la8p6.jpg&h=ae5a87e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■環保斗壓毀地下行人路的玻璃簷篷。李家傑攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨凌晨1時許，一批工人在銅鑼灣利舞臺廣場22樓天台，利用一條吊臂將一個面積約2.4米乘1.7米、裝有冷氣系統零件的環保斗吊上天台，以便進行中央冷氣工程，當環保斗被吊至頂樓時，吊臂突然出現摺曲及傾側，並撞向頂樓及天台欄杆，環保斗飛脫凌空墮地，壓毀地下行人路的玻璃簷篷，並扯斷一條用作固定電車電纜的鋼索，現場地面滿佈碎片，幸好當時無人車輛經過，否則後果堪虞。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180328/large/a0905a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180328%2Flarge%2Fa0905a.gif&h=55888716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■吊臂將環保斗吊至頂樓時，突然摺曲及傾側撞向天台欄杆，令環保斗墮地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跑馬地電車服務一度暫停<br />\n<br />\n警方事後封鎖現場，以便工入搶救及善後，電車公司亦派員維修損毀電纜，並暫停跑馬地的電車服務，警方開放利舞臺廣場對開波斯富街慢線行車。<br />\n<br />\n電車公司稱，一條用作固定電車電纜的輔助線在事故中受損，需要進行搶修，而公司按警方要求，暫時關閉了涉事路段電網，並拆除部份輔助線讓吊臂車進入該路段範圍進行清理善後工作，至昨晚10時，該路段電車服務恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n利舞臺廣場所屬的希慎興業有限公司企業傳訊部稱，有關承辦商正審視各項細節，並將會提交詳細報告予希慎。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李家傑、司徒韋桐  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n力谷網購　仍蝕逾2億<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n隨倒冧棚架5米高墮下工人1死1傷　承建商屢因同類意外被控"},{"pid":"c049099cfd13905da7037b28b70101e715f8ec6f","tid":608295,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:37:28.000Z","msg":"好在凌晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da66983c0d64009750efa5fdd24190ea006629e6","tid":608295,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"好撚恐怖<br />\n平時出街見到呢d 高空吊物都會走開d"},{"pid":"93061f627229a51ec4db94db707de06efdf44743","tid":608295,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"條電纜斷左周圍發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ac17b1286bd58215542637bb8913d491b50db2","tid":608295,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93061f627229a51ec4db94db707de06efdf44743","tid":608295,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"條電纜斷左周圍發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T05:25:45.000Z","msg":"鬼船"},{"pid":"002c69c893809b2b6904acc654a385a9c3785312","tid":608295,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T07:12:40.000Z","msg":"係咪用吊船機吊環保斗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f795fbd1f93bc94e8ee08fca15983ed9d3e4e77","tid":608295,"uid":65408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T07:19:49.000Z","msg":"發生響日頭嘅話真係唔知會死幾多人"},{"pid":"